            <h1>Angular Demo Angular的作用范围 $timeout 与 setTimeout</h1>
            <hr>
        </div>

        <div class="col-sm-8">
            <h4>使用setTimeout {{ demo12.data.setTimeOutMessage }}
                <button class="btn btn-default" ng-click="demo12.event.changeSetTimeOutMessage()">点击后 2秒后显示改变</button>
            </h4>

            <h4>使用setTimeout 与 scope apply {{ demo12.data.setTimeOutMessage2 }}
                <button class="btn btn-default" ng-click="demo12.event.changeSetTimeOutMessage2()">点击后 2秒后显示改变</button>
            </h4>

            <h4>使用$timeout {{ demo12.data.angularTimeOutMessage }}
                <button class="btn btn-default" ng-click="demo12.event.changeAngularTimeOutMessage()">点击后 2秒后显示改变
                </button>
            </h4>

            <p class="bg-info"><a href="http://jimhoskins.com/2012/12/17/angularjs-and-apply.html">相关文章: angularjs and
                    scope apply</a></p>
            <hr>
        </div>
    </div>


